India’s Essar to Buy Shell’s Stanlow Refinery, Reuters Reports

-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 
2011-02-17T05:17:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/india-s-essar-to-buy-shell-s-stanlow-refinery-reuters-reports.html
  India ’s  Essar Oil Ltd . may pay as
much as $400 million to acquire  Royal Dutch Shell Plc ’s refinery
at Stanlow in the U.K., Reuters reported, citing two people
familiar with the deal.  Terms have been agreed and an announcement is expected any
time, the news service said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  